{"tid":1551639,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［推到聯合國出聲］請到紐約總部請願示威","createTime":"2019-09-08T05:50:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T07:26:35.000Z","uid":172102,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3417274aa4577fc02c6bc481b4fe4a455dfb986a","tid":1551639,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"第一次出Post，請屌得細力啲。<br />\n<br />\n今日見到女何妖份抹黑香港人嘅野，用唔知咩特權上到General Assembly，火都黎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： <br />\n何超瓊偷偷地向聯合國誣衊示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551126</a><br />\n<br />\n但同時提醒咗，我地要加大聯合國戰線力度，較早係7月，已經有連登巴打親身去信過總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但好似未聽到有回覆同無咩Noise:<br />\n【突發】直踩聯合國總部揭露警方暴行！信已接收！Fact Checked！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1324663\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1324663</a><br />\n<br />\n咁到底點樣搞聯合國線先會上到報呢？參考翻搞氣候變化罷課行動搞得有聲有色嘅九歲瑞典妹妹：<br />\n<img src=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Greta_Thunberg_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3AGreta_Thunberg_4.jpg&h=d28e2aa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://timedotcom.files.wordpress.com/2019/08/greta-thunberg-climate-protest-un.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimedotcom.files.wordpress.com%2F2019%2F08%2Fgreta-thunberg-climate-protest-un.jpg&h=af2cb080&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢帶領全球一班細路同年輕人罷課成功獲得國際關注，令好多政治人物同荷里活明星都出聲聲援。而呢位妹妹最近八月三十日親身飛到美國約紐聯合國總部遊行，得就多間外媒嘅廣泛報導：<a href=\"https://time.com/5665835/greta-thunberg-united-nations-protest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftime.com%2F5665835%2Fgreta-thunberg-united-nations-protest%2F&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprhvMbnGxJ%2B6Vh8biNj9iadw%3D&h=e9d6d8c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://time.com/5665835/greta-thunberg-united-nations-protest/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議所有係美國附近嘅巴絲，有組織地搞翻場請願示威，事前邀請外媒到場採訪。由於香港反送中行動嘅有地區性同政治性局限，未推到國際同人權層面，外國人未必會關注咁多。所以我建議如果要推到國際化啲，可以主打以下兩個重點：<br />\n1. 政治打壓，香港人人權受剝奪<br />\n2. Police Brutality<br />\n3 Humanitarian Crisis <br />\n<br />\n如果搵到小朋友拎住個slogan 咁樣行出黎，效果當然更好，但我身為成年人都唔想再見到小朋友要行咁前。<br />\n<br />\n文宣方面，大家暫時都局限左自己係自己page、account 到，反而唔識好好利用去啲有100K follower以上嘅Page 到留言洗板。你可能會話洗人板會令人反感，但其實係最快最多人見到嘅方法，外國都好興咁樣係啲post到comment 一個時事議題叫人推上去top comment。<br />\n<br />\n以下係一啲文宣可以做嘅英文Template，最好有數字，同重點宣傳一啲嚴重嘅Case，依家我所見嘅一係一張圖好多格好多單咁放埋一齊，啲英文字又細隻，有啲難消化。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGoKtCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGoKtCY.jpg&h=4f3077a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKyRS4E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKyRS4E.png&h=b978d5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PCpxCwj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPCpxCwj.jpg&h=b23d1eae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖則聯合國左膠，但希望大家唔好睇小佢，做得嘅都要做！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港<br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"835ee0f0bcafb2de4c6fb8ac7d5c5fd1bfc1dd27","tid":1551639,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3417274aa4577fc02c6bc481b4fe4a455dfb986a","tid":1551639,"uid":172102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:50:29.000Z","msg":"第一次出Post，請屌得細力啲。<br />\n<br />\n今日見到女何妖份抹黑香港人嘅野，用唔知咩特權上到General Assembly，火都黎埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />： <br />\n何超瓊偷偷地向聯合國誣衊示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551126\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551126</a><br />\n<br />\n但同時提醒咗，我地要加大聯合國戰線力度，較早係7月，已經有連登巴打親身去信過總部<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但好似未聽到有回覆同無咩Noise:<br />\n【突發】直踩聯合國總部揭露警方暴行！信已接收